1
00:01:25,910 --> 00:01:35,000
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

2
00:01:35,420 --> 00:01:37,940
[Episode 30]

3
00:01:38,479 --> 00:01:40,610
You're interested in paintings, huh?

4
00:01:48,229 --> 00:01:50,030
Where did you get this painting?

5
00:01:50,140 --> 00:01:51,070
I just bought it.

6
00:01:51,430 --> 00:01:52,890
Then, Miss Luo, do you know

7
00:01:53,140 --> 00:01:55,070
who the artist of this painting is?

8
00:01:55,370 --> 00:01:56,310
I don't know.

9
00:01:57,420 --> 00:01:58,560
But I do know that

10
00:01:58,560 --> 00:01:59,729
with the brushstrokes

11
00:01:59,729 --> 00:02:01,190
and feel of this painting,

12
00:02:01,500 --> 00:02:03,340
it's bound to be priceless.

13
00:02:04,930 --> 00:02:06,830
An artist of exceptional talent

14
00:02:06,950 --> 00:02:08,949
will not stay in obscurity forever.

15
00:02:09,620 --> 00:02:11,430
A true friend is never far away...

16
00:02:11,430 --> 00:02:12,690
-What?
-Master Cao...

17
00:02:13,020 --> 00:02:14,150
We should get going.

18
00:02:16,590 --> 00:02:17,920
I won't see you out then.

19
00:02:19,090 --> 00:02:19,690
Goodbye.

20
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:27,710
Miss Luo.

21
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:29,870
What I'm about to say

22
00:02:29,870 --> 00:02:31,460
might be a little presumptuous.

23
00:02:31,460 --> 00:02:33,090
From the look of your complexion,

24
00:02:33,090 --> 00:02:34,960
I think you might have

25
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:35,780
a minor health issue.

26
00:02:35,780 --> 00:02:37,910
I'll help you nurse it if you have time.

27
00:02:38,300 --> 00:02:39,400
Am I sick?

28
00:02:39,530 --> 00:02:40,260
Don't worry,

29
00:02:40,710 --> 00:02:42,310
I can help you take care of it.

30
00:02:43,970 --> 00:02:45,700
Then I won't stand on ceremony.

31
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,840
I'll go see you when I'm free.

32
00:02:49,470 --> 00:02:50,560
I'd recommend sooner rather than later.

33
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:52,750
Nursing health issues
shouldn't be delayed.

34
00:02:52,750 --> 00:02:54,150
Here is my business card.

35
00:02:55,690 --> 00:02:56,970
[Cao Ye, Chairman]

36
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:02,910
Master Cao, this way.

37
00:03:14,190 --> 00:03:15,240
Thank you, Ranran.

38
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:16,570
Thanks so much, Ranran.

39
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:17,860
Don't mention it.

40
00:03:17,860 --> 00:03:19,120
That's because your restaurant

41
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:20,380
makes delicious food.

42
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:21,240
You flatter us.

43
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:22,000
I'll get back to work then.

44
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:22,740
Keep in touch.

45
00:03:22,740 --> 00:03:23,430
Keep in touch.

46
00:03:23,430 --> 00:03:25,230
Let me know if you need anything.

47
00:03:30,750 --> 00:03:31,440
Liang.

48
00:03:31,890 --> 00:03:32,310
Liang.

49
00:03:32,310 --> 00:03:33,260
Come out and help. Hurry.

50
00:03:33,260 --> 00:03:34,400
-It's so busy out here.
-I’m coming.

51
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:35,020
Can't you read the room?

52
00:03:35,020 --> 00:03:35,680
Here you go.

53
00:03:35,790 --> 00:03:36,190
Okay.

54
00:03:36,190 --> 00:03:37,060
Thank you.

55
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:38,500
Hurry up!

56
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:39,350
Coming.

57
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:40,960
Easy, easy.

58
00:03:53,480 --> 00:03:55,010
Okay, I'll get that for you.

59
00:04:00,030 --> 00:04:00,800
Bonjour.

60
00:04:02,580 --> 00:04:03,980
What are you doing here?

61
00:04:04,090 --> 00:04:05,870
I didn't want you to work hard alone.

62
00:04:05,870 --> 00:04:06,960
Tao, hurry up.

63
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,330
The guests are waiting.

64
00:04:08,370 --> 00:04:08,930
Coming.

65
00:04:10,650 --> 00:04:11,360
Here, here.

66
00:04:13,070 --> 00:04:13,930
Chili, please.

67
00:04:14,010 --> 00:04:15,140
Let me get it for you.

68
00:04:16,209 --> 00:04:17,070
-Kitchen, be quick.
-Okay.

69
00:04:17,070 --> 00:04:18,670
We have a lot of guests today.

70
00:04:26,630 --> 00:04:27,570
Thank you.

71
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,260
Here you go.

72
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:29,430
Enjoy your meal.

73
00:04:29,980 --> 00:04:31,430
No more dishes to serve.
I'll get back to washing.

74
00:04:31,430 --> 00:04:32,290
Okay.

75
00:04:34,370 --> 00:04:35,230
How is the food?

76
00:04:35,250 --> 00:04:36,060
Pretty good.

77
00:04:36,130 --> 00:04:37,240
Then let's

78
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:38,159
meet at 1:00 p.m.

79
00:04:38,159 --> 00:04:39,930
at the restaurant entrance on time.

80
00:04:39,930 --> 00:04:41,060
I'll go pay the bill.

81
00:04:43,760 --> 00:04:45,480
These 3 tables are all our clients.

82
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:46,890
Calculate them together
and give us a discount.

83
00:04:46,890 --> 00:04:47,870
Yes, I've been told to do so.

84
00:04:47,870 --> 00:04:48,580
Thank you.

85
00:05:34,370 --> 00:05:36,820
Time to eat, Boss Xu.

86
00:05:37,890 --> 00:05:38,560
Hurry up.

87
00:05:40,740 --> 00:05:41,570
Mr. Jia's distribution for us in Russia

88
00:05:41,570 --> 00:05:43,040
this time

89
00:05:43,070 --> 00:05:44,130
was a huge success.

90
00:05:44,190 --> 00:05:45,700
Shouldn't we celebrate?

91
00:05:45,860 --> 00:05:47,100
Of course we should.

92
00:05:48,500 --> 00:05:49,180
Come on.

93
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:50,250
Come on.

94
00:05:50,570 --> 00:05:51,180
Cheers.

95
00:05:51,510 --> 00:05:52,940
First battle won.

96
00:05:53,130 --> 00:05:54,000
Keep up the momentum!

97
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,200
Keep up the momentum!

98
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:00,690
Let's eat.

99
00:06:00,690 --> 00:06:01,130
Wait.

100
00:06:01,500 --> 00:06:02,310
Before we eat,

101
00:06:02,330 --> 00:06:03,920
could you sign the contract,

102
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:04,860
Boss Zhuang,

103
00:06:04,890 --> 00:06:06,310
and a few remittance forms?

104
00:06:06,310 --> 00:06:07,400
Let's eat first.

105
00:06:07,620 --> 00:06:08,750
Just sign them first, please.

106
00:06:08,750 --> 00:06:10,180
Then we can eat in peace.

107
00:06:10,300 --> 00:06:11,030
Here you are.

108
00:06:13,690 --> 00:06:15,420
I spent all afternoon cooking.

109
00:06:17,900 --> 00:06:19,050
[Remittance Advice]

110
00:06:22,490 --> 00:06:24,390
[Remittance Advice]

111
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:26,360
[Purchase Contract]

112
00:06:25,770 --> 00:06:27,040
Why are there so many?

113
00:06:26,540 --> 00:06:29,130
[Property Purchase Contract]

114
00:06:30,170 --> 00:06:31,830
Property Purchase Contract?

115
00:06:34,080 --> 00:06:34,940
[Contract] [Party A: Xu Yang]
[Party B: Zhuang Zhuang]

116
00:06:35,159 --> 00:06:36,600
You bought this place?

117
00:06:36,620 --> 00:06:37,950
Just one last step,

118
00:06:38,350 --> 00:06:41,170
which is the owner's signature.

119
00:06:42,070 --> 00:06:42,690
Come on.

120
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:44,340
The final page.

121
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:47,280
Sign here.

122
00:06:52,740 --> 00:06:53,370
But...

123
00:06:54,010 --> 00:06:55,480
why is only my name on it?

124
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:54,990
[Property Purchase Contract]

125
00:06:55,110 --> 00:06:56,350
[Contract] [Party A: Xu Yang]
[Party B: Zhuang Zhuang]

126
00:06:57,770 --> 00:06:58,860
I was worried

127
00:06:58,890 --> 00:06:59,900
if we argue later

128
00:06:59,930 --> 00:07:00,450
and you kick me out,

129
00:07:00,450 --> 00:07:01,580
I'd talk back to you.

130
00:07:02,370 --> 00:07:03,220
If my name wasn't on it,

131
00:07:03,220 --> 00:07:04,240
you'd dare talk back?

132
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:05,170
I wouldn't dare.

133
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:07,260
Alright, just sign it.

134
00:07:09,470 --> 00:07:11,150
[Party B: Signature: Zhuang Zhuang]

135
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:16,680
We finally

136
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:18,040
have our own home.

137
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:22,660
We finally have a home in Beijing.

138
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:35,750
Hello.

139
00:07:36,420 --> 00:07:37,120
Sophia.

140
00:07:37,810 --> 00:07:38,810
How have you been?

141
00:07:39,510 --> 00:07:40,620
Everything is great.

142
00:07:40,620 --> 00:07:41,680
Zhuang Zhuang mentioned you

143
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:42,580
to me yesterday.

144
00:07:42,580 --> 00:07:43,710
You two should chat.

145
00:07:43,980 --> 00:07:45,680
Okay, I miss her too.

146
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:46,330
Sophia.

147
00:07:46,890 --> 00:07:48,050
Hello, Sophia.

148
00:07:48,300 --> 00:07:49,760
How's your health lately?

149
00:07:50,070 --> 00:07:50,800
Pretty good.

150
00:07:50,950 --> 00:07:52,810
I really miss you, Zhuang Zhuang.

151
00:07:54,370 --> 00:07:56,230
Did you receive the down jackets?

152
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:57,100
Yes, I did.

153
00:07:57,390 --> 00:07:59,370
They look very warm.

154
00:07:59,830 --> 00:08:01,690
They will definitely be popular.

155
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:03,660
That's good.

156
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:04,540
However,

157
00:08:04,930 --> 00:08:06,740
I know making this compromise

158
00:08:06,740 --> 00:08:07,870
must be hard for you.

159
00:08:08,060 --> 00:08:08,860
But it's okay.

160
00:08:09,010 --> 00:08:10,610
Everything has a beginning.

161
00:08:10,660 --> 00:08:11,590
What do you mean?

162
00:08:12,450 --> 00:08:13,700
All your down jackets

163
00:08:13,810 --> 00:08:15,620
are labeled "Made in Italy."

164
00:08:15,980 --> 00:08:17,390
Didn't you know it?

165
00:08:20,220 --> 00:08:21,800
I'm not really clear on the details.

166
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:22,970
I'll ask Shengli.

167
00:08:23,630 --> 00:08:24,130
Okay.

168
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:25,240
Alright.

169
00:08:25,510 --> 00:08:27,370
Take good care of yourself.

170
00:08:28,250 --> 00:08:29,010
You too.

171
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,540
Okay, bye.

172
00:08:31,930 --> 00:08:32,730
What's wrong?

173
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,600
Mr. Jia relabeled

174
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:36,330
our clothes.

175
00:08:37,030 --> 00:08:38,159
That's impossible.

176
00:08:38,409 --> 00:08:40,080
It's clearly stated in the contract.

177
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:42,000
Sophia said the clothes she received

178
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:43,860
were all labeled "Made in Italy."

179
00:08:52,510 --> 00:08:53,370
Hello, Mr. Jia.

180
00:08:53,820 --> 00:08:54,390
Didn't we

181
00:08:54,410 --> 00:08:55,740
make it clear back then?

182
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:58,250
It's also clearly stated in the contract.

183
00:08:58,250 --> 00:08:58,840
Why on earth

184
00:08:58,840 --> 00:08:59,630
have you put "Made in Italy"

185
00:08:59,630 --> 00:09:00,680
on our clothes?

186
00:09:01,290 --> 00:09:02,600
The goods are in my hands.

187
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:03,910
I can sell them however I want.

188
00:09:03,910 --> 00:09:04,920
That's fraud!

189
00:09:05,150 --> 00:09:06,750
This is a breach of contract.

190
00:09:07,500 --> 00:09:09,050
If I sell them with Chinese labels,

191
00:09:09,050 --> 00:09:10,390
nobody will buy them.

192
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:12,200
I paid you

193
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:13,500
for the goods.

194
00:09:13,620 --> 00:09:14,150
I can't just let my inventory

195
00:09:14,150 --> 00:09:15,350
go to waste, can I?

196
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:17,410
Who's going to compensate for my loss?

197
00:09:17,410 --> 00:09:18,740
No matter what it takes,

198
00:09:18,890 --> 00:09:19,510
putting the money

199
00:09:19,510 --> 00:09:20,910
in your own pocket first,

200
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:22,650
that's the way of doing business.

201
00:09:22,650 --> 00:09:24,310
What you're doing is illegal.

202
00:09:24,630 --> 00:09:25,560
I'm telling you,

203
00:09:25,870 --> 00:09:27,930
we are terminating our cooperation.

204
00:09:31,650 --> 00:09:32,980
It was all written in the contract,

205
00:09:32,980 --> 00:09:34,050
clearly stated.

206
00:09:34,050 --> 00:09:35,110
How dare he do this?

207
00:09:36,030 --> 00:09:37,510
He really stoops so low.

208
00:09:38,030 --> 00:09:39,630
It's harder than we imagined

209
00:09:39,740 --> 00:09:41,220
to stick to our own brand.

210
00:09:41,910 --> 00:09:43,920
This next batch of clothes

211
00:09:43,940 --> 00:09:45,570
is about to leave the factory.

212
00:09:45,570 --> 00:09:46,900
We can only look for some

213
00:09:46,910 --> 00:09:48,550
small-scale independent retailers.

214
00:09:48,550 --> 00:09:50,130
We can definitely sell them.

215
00:09:50,130 --> 00:09:51,790
Our clothes are of good quality.

216
00:09:51,790 --> 00:09:52,920
But the cycle

217
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:54,140
will be prolonged.

218
00:09:54,530 --> 00:09:55,130
And we're about to

219
00:09:55,130 --> 00:09:56,750
pay the factory workers' wages.

220
00:09:56,750 --> 00:09:57,290
There's also

221
00:09:57,290 --> 00:09:59,350
the raw material cost they advanced.

222
00:09:59,410 --> 00:10:01,140
I learned this before at Ruhua.

223
00:10:02,150 --> 00:10:04,610
A signature can double the value
of a design.

224
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:06,930
A brand logo

225
00:10:07,290 --> 00:10:09,220
can determine the value of an item.

226
00:10:09,650 --> 00:10:10,600
But if we

227
00:10:10,630 --> 00:10:12,440
don't stick with building our brand,

228
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:13,540
all our efforts

229
00:10:13,740 --> 00:10:15,360
will just end up a one-off deal.

230
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:16,290
How about this?

231
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:19,520
Let's transfer some profit

232
00:10:19,630 --> 00:10:21,230
from the shoe factory first.

233
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:22,630
We can't owe wages.

234
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:25,890
This afternoon, I'll contact

235
00:10:25,890 --> 00:10:28,050
the shoe distributors and
market representatives

236
00:10:28,050 --> 00:10:29,450
we've been working with.

237
00:10:29,510 --> 00:10:31,370
See if they can help find a way out.

238
00:10:31,620 --> 00:10:32,600
We know these people

239
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:33,860
pretty well.

240
00:10:34,570 --> 00:10:35,220
They're also

241
00:10:35,220 --> 00:10:36,850
sincerely wanting Chinese goods

242
00:10:36,850 --> 00:10:38,300
to make a name overseas.

243
00:10:38,560 --> 00:10:41,020
Let's help each other out
at a time like this.

244
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:41,910
Alright.

245
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:43,600
Let's not think about it for now.

246
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:44,530
Let's eat first.

247
00:10:54,340 --> 00:10:55,910
Doesn't Zongbao always say

248
00:10:56,410 --> 00:10:58,830
"every obstacle can be overcome"?

249
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:02,030
You have me.

250
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:14,970
Bro, you're back.

251
00:11:15,190 --> 00:11:16,360
Perfect timing. I'm going out for a bit.

252
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:17,490
Where are you going?

253
00:11:17,530 --> 00:11:18,550
I'm going to the basement storage.

254
00:11:18,550 --> 00:11:19,510
There will be customers

255
00:11:19,510 --> 00:11:20,240
coming to pick up goods tomorrow.

256
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,580
I'll go and register for an appointment.

257
00:11:21,580 --> 00:11:22,980
What's in this envelope?

258
00:11:25,030 --> 00:11:25,720
This...

259
00:11:26,360 --> 00:11:27,130
The registration form.

260
00:11:27,130 --> 00:11:28,310
But we need two copies, right?

261
00:11:28,310 --> 00:11:30,080
Otherwise, security won't have a backup.

262
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:31,100
I remember

263
00:11:31,790 --> 00:11:33,850
we registered yesterday, didn't we?

264
00:11:34,580 --> 00:11:36,150
Yes, we did,

265
00:11:36,170 --> 00:11:37,030
but we also need to give one copy

266
00:11:37,030 --> 00:11:38,250
to security.

267
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:38,970
Otherwise, tomorrow morning,

268
00:11:38,970 --> 00:11:40,060
he won't let us in.

269
00:11:40,290 --> 00:11:41,270
Okay, go ahead.

270
00:11:41,460 --> 00:11:42,120
Okay.

271
00:11:43,170 --> 00:11:44,030
By the way, bro,

272
00:11:44,750 --> 00:11:46,810
the suppliers have all contacted us.

273
00:11:46,820 --> 00:11:48,360
The sales reps for leather shoes

274
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:49,970
were really a big help this time.

275
00:11:49,970 --> 00:11:50,530
Our goods

276
00:11:50,530 --> 00:11:51,720
are famous in Russia.

277
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:51,980
Everyone knows

278
00:11:51,980 --> 00:11:53,510
we're a good Chinese brand.

279
00:11:54,290 --> 00:11:55,750
But can the factory

280
00:11:55,770 --> 00:11:57,170
keep up with production?

281
00:11:57,550 --> 00:11:58,220
The latest batch

282
00:11:58,220 --> 00:12:00,480
won't be ready until the end of December.

283
00:12:01,010 --> 00:12:02,580
It's fine, I'll talk to them.

284
00:12:02,580 --> 00:12:04,440
Good things are worth waiting for.

285
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:05,030
Bro, Sis,

286
00:12:05,340 --> 00:12:05,960
thanks to your decision

287
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:07,160
to persist back then,

288
00:12:07,480 --> 00:12:08,200
we really made it

289
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:09,970
through this crisis.

290
00:12:10,620 --> 00:12:11,240
I'll get back to work.

291
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:12,100
Okay, go ahead.

292
00:12:12,580 --> 00:12:14,040
Thanks for your hard work.

293
00:12:16,520 --> 00:12:18,720
Running around all day, you must be tired.

294
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:19,320
Not at all.

295
00:12:19,770 --> 00:12:20,530
Not at all?

296
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:22,670
Shipping the goods out

297
00:12:22,670 --> 00:12:23,910
will be a relief.

298
00:12:25,370 --> 00:12:26,910
Now that we've hired more workers,

299
00:12:26,910 --> 00:12:28,510
the volume has gone right up.

300
00:12:28,550 --> 00:12:30,220
Yes, volume goes up,

301
00:12:30,270 --> 00:12:32,150
but we can't let quality slip.

302
00:12:32,860 --> 00:12:33,290
I think

303
00:12:33,290 --> 00:12:35,950
we should visit the factory
before the New Year.

304
00:12:35,980 --> 00:12:37,990
To hand out some New Year gifts,

305
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:39,790
and most importantly,

306
00:12:39,870 --> 00:12:41,240
to make sure overtime pay is settled.

307
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:42,150
That'll keep everyone

308
00:12:42,150 --> 00:12:43,800
motivated to work hard.

309
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:45,180
Sure.

310
00:12:45,510 --> 00:12:46,100
Then tomorrow,

311
00:12:46,100 --> 00:12:47,560
I'll go shopping with you.

312
00:12:47,700 --> 00:12:48,360
Okay.

313
00:12:53,620 --> 00:12:55,940
Mr. Chen, here is what you asked for.

314
00:12:59,940 --> 00:13:00,790
For their down jackets,

315
00:13:00,790 --> 00:13:02,890
the raw materials and craftsmanship used

316
00:13:02,890 --> 00:13:04,090
are all written on it.

317
00:13:04,170 --> 00:13:04,770
However, for some

318
00:13:04,770 --> 00:13:06,210
specially customized items,

319
00:13:06,210 --> 00:13:06,770
you'll need to contact

320
00:13:06,770 --> 00:13:07,860
their suppliers.

321
00:13:08,530 --> 00:13:10,310
I've also prepared the supplier list.

322
00:13:10,310 --> 00:13:11,320
It's at the back.

323
00:13:14,430 --> 00:13:15,330
Good job.

324
00:13:29,180 --> 00:13:30,840
All right, this is far enough.

325
00:13:31,080 --> 00:13:32,710
Thanks everyone for your hard work.

326
00:13:32,710 --> 00:13:33,370
We still need to

327
00:13:33,370 --> 00:13:34,740
ensure safe production.

328
00:13:34,740 --> 00:13:35,220
If you have any questions,

329
00:13:35,220 --> 00:13:36,340
feel free to contact us anytime.

330
00:13:36,340 --> 00:13:37,470
Look at you two.

331
00:13:37,500 --> 00:13:39,220
You're so busy with sales
before the New Year,

332
00:13:39,220 --> 00:13:40,180
yet you made a special trip

333
00:13:40,180 --> 00:13:41,060
to see us.

334
00:13:41,210 --> 00:13:42,810
All right, don't mention it.

335
00:13:43,050 --> 00:13:44,510
We only exist because of the factory.

336
00:13:44,510 --> 00:13:46,840
The factory is the foundation
of everything we have.

337
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:47,940
The cafeteria has food ready.

338
00:13:47,940 --> 00:13:48,480
Grab a quick bite

339
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:49,510
It won't take much time.

340
00:13:49,510 --> 00:13:50,630
We really appreciate it,

341
00:13:50,630 --> 00:13:51,340
but the two of us

342
00:13:51,340 --> 00:13:52,690
still have to go to 2 other factories.

343
00:13:52,690 --> 00:13:53,910
We have to hurry on the way.

344
00:13:53,910 --> 00:13:55,620
All right, I won't keep you then.

345
00:13:55,620 --> 00:13:56,340
Drive safely.

346
00:13:56,340 --> 00:13:57,270
Have a safe trip.

347
00:13:57,590 --> 00:13:59,120
Leave the production to us.

348
00:13:59,530 --> 00:14:00,470
Rest assured.

349
00:14:00,530 --> 00:14:00,770
Okay.

350
00:14:00,770 --> 00:14:01,320
We will.

351
00:14:01,690 --> 00:14:03,150
Happy New Year in advance.

352
00:14:03,740 --> 00:14:04,340
Happy New Year.

353
00:14:04,340 --> 00:14:05,200
Happy New Year.

354
00:14:05,910 --> 00:14:07,200
Okay, I won't see you out.

355
00:14:07,200 --> 00:14:07,760
I'll leave you to it.

356
00:14:07,760 --> 00:14:08,260
Bye.

357
00:14:08,290 --> 00:14:09,410
-Bye.
-Thanks for your hard work.

358
00:14:09,410 --> 00:14:09,960
Bye.

359
00:14:13,210 --> 00:14:14,650
Should we finish it

360
00:14:14,670 --> 00:14:16,330
all at once these 2 days, or...

361
00:14:16,370 --> 00:14:17,000
Since we're already out here,

362
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:18,400
let's finish it in one go.

363
00:14:18,630 --> 00:14:20,490
I'm just afraid you'll get tired.

364
00:14:20,630 --> 00:14:21,750
Everyone is working so hard.

365
00:14:21,750 --> 00:14:23,680
We have nothing to complain about.

366
00:14:24,170 --> 00:14:25,200
Okay. When we go back this time,

367
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:27,000
let's do the accounts properly.

368
00:14:27,100 --> 00:14:27,900
This time,

369
00:14:27,920 --> 00:14:28,980
because we need to rush
this batch of goods,

370
00:14:28,980 --> 00:14:29,960
we hired a lot of extra workers.

371
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:31,220
But the efficiency

372
00:14:31,330 --> 00:14:32,990
has improved significantly.

373
00:14:34,100 --> 00:14:35,140
After this trip,

374
00:14:35,160 --> 00:14:36,270
let's not go back to Beijing.

375
00:14:36,270 --> 00:14:37,570
Let's go back to our hometowns.

376
00:14:37,570 --> 00:14:38,930
We have to deliver the goods
after the New Year.

377
00:14:38,930 --> 00:14:39,970
Let's not go back this year.

378
00:14:39,970 --> 00:14:41,430
Two days won't make a difference.

379
00:14:41,430 --> 00:14:42,600
Everyone is busy with production.

380
00:14:42,600 --> 00:14:44,330
It's no use for us to just worry.

381
00:14:45,510 --> 00:14:46,930
We'll stay for 2 days,

382
00:14:47,080 --> 00:14:47,820
just 2 days.

383
00:14:48,500 --> 00:14:49,190
Okay.

384
00:14:49,350 --> 00:14:51,090
Then we'll go back to Wenzhou first,

385
00:14:51,090 --> 00:14:52,150
and then back to...

386
00:14:52,900 --> 00:14:53,990
-Yantai.
-Yantai.

387
00:15:02,460 --> 00:15:03,450
Look at you.

388
00:15:03,480 --> 00:15:04,250
You bring so many things

389
00:15:04,250 --> 00:15:05,370
every time you come back.

390
00:15:05,370 --> 00:15:06,410
Let Shengli take care of them.

391
00:15:06,410 --> 00:15:07,030
Come over here.

392
00:15:07,030 --> 00:15:07,920
Sweetheart,

393
00:15:07,940 --> 00:15:08,760
Zhuang Zhuang,

394
00:15:08,760 --> 00:15:09,530
sit here and rest.

395
00:15:09,530 --> 00:15:10,790
Come, have some water.

396
00:15:10,850 --> 00:15:11,910
Thank you, Auntie.

397
00:15:12,070 --> 00:15:12,640
Auntie,

398
00:15:13,340 --> 00:15:15,320
these are clothes my mom made

399
00:15:15,340 --> 00:15:16,340
for you and Uncle.

400
00:15:16,490 --> 00:15:17,620
See if you like them.

401
00:15:17,700 --> 00:15:19,750
A new piece of clothing every year.

402
00:15:19,750 --> 00:15:20,550
Thank your mom.

403
00:15:20,550 --> 00:15:22,600
-She makes one for me every year.
-You're welcome. It's no trouble.

404
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:23,600
I tried it just now.

405
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:25,600
-It fits perfectly.
-Do you like it?

406
00:15:25,620 --> 00:15:26,600
Say hello to your parents.

407
00:15:26,600 --> 00:15:27,390
I did.

408
00:15:27,530 --> 00:15:28,990
They said hello to you too.

409
00:15:29,790 --> 00:15:31,650
-Thank them.
-The dishes are almost ready.

410
00:15:31,650 --> 00:15:33,110
Shall we start the dinner?

411
00:15:33,410 --> 00:15:33,910
Yes.

412
00:15:34,340 --> 00:15:35,200
By the way, Zhuang Zhuang.

413
00:15:35,200 --> 00:15:36,070
You know what?

414
00:15:36,100 --> 00:15:37,420
Do you smell that?

415
00:15:37,440 --> 00:15:39,120
Your uncle remembers that
you loved the flatfish

416
00:15:39,120 --> 00:15:40,480
last time you were here.

417
00:15:40,530 --> 00:15:41,980
He's already stewing it for you.

418
00:15:41,980 --> 00:15:43,000
Smells so good.

419
00:15:43,030 --> 00:15:43,740
Whatever you want to eat
these couple of days,

420
00:15:43,740 --> 00:15:44,990
just tell him.

421
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:45,500
Okay.

422
00:15:45,530 --> 00:15:46,280
Let him make it for you.

423
00:15:46,280 --> 00:15:47,440
-Nourish yourself.
-Yeah, I’ll cook for you.

424
00:15:47,440 --> 00:15:49,500
Then I'll just have my usual 3 dishes.

425
00:15:49,910 --> 00:15:51,680
-You?
-What does it have to do with you?

426
00:15:51,680 --> 00:15:52,250
Exactly.

427
00:15:52,250 --> 00:15:53,440
We're talking about
what Zhuang Zhuang likes to eat,

428
00:15:53,440 --> 00:15:54,000
okay?

429
00:15:54,240 --> 00:15:54,940
Okay.

430
00:15:54,960 --> 00:15:56,310
Thank you, Uncle and Auntie.

431
00:15:56,310 --> 00:15:57,650
Go check on your fish.

432
00:15:57,670 --> 00:15:58,730
Don't let it burn.

433
00:15:58,770 --> 00:15:59,220
Yes, yes.

434
00:15:59,220 --> 00:15:59,630
Go, go.

435
00:15:59,670 --> 00:16:00,430
Hurry up.

436
00:16:00,500 --> 00:16:01,460
Hurry.

437
00:16:01,510 --> 00:16:02,550
Okay.

438
00:16:06,030 --> 00:16:07,220
Zhuang Zhuang,

439
00:16:08,270 --> 00:16:09,100
when you two came back this time,

440
00:16:09,100 --> 00:16:11,350
I noticed you both look a bit thinner.

441
00:16:11,700 --> 00:16:13,410
Did you not eat well in Beijing?

442
00:16:13,410 --> 00:16:15,250
Did you not take good care of yourselves?

443
00:16:15,250 --> 00:16:17,000
We were a bit busy lately.

444
00:16:17,790 --> 00:16:19,650
We'll definitely eat well later.

445
00:16:19,980 --> 00:16:22,370
Yes, take good care of yourselves.

446
00:16:22,860 --> 00:16:24,770
Shengli, how's the garlic?

447
00:16:24,870 --> 00:16:25,940
-Hurry up.
-Done.

448
00:16:26,460 --> 00:16:27,650
Haven't you mashed it yet?  Hurry.

449
00:16:27,650 --> 00:16:28,600
I'm so happy

450
00:16:28,630 --> 00:16:30,180
you're back.

451
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:31,360
Look at your uncle.

452
00:16:31,360 --> 00:16:32,720
He's also thrilled.

453
00:16:33,120 --> 00:16:34,980
We'll come back often in the future.

454
00:16:34,980 --> 00:16:36,000
Definitely.

455
00:16:39,130 --> 00:16:40,240
Honey.

456
00:16:40,260 --> 00:16:41,360
Coming.

457
00:16:41,940 --> 00:16:42,460
Didn't you say

458
00:16:42,460 --> 00:16:44,320
you wanted to eat more cucumber shreds?

459
00:16:44,320 --> 00:16:45,580
I cut some more for you.

460
00:16:45,630 --> 00:16:46,360
Here you are.

461
00:16:47,130 --> 00:16:48,080
Have a try.

462
00:16:48,320 --> 00:16:49,100
Let me try.

463
00:16:51,620 --> 00:16:53,170
Eat slowly, don't choke.

464
00:16:54,290 --> 00:16:55,580
I was so mad today.

465
00:16:55,580 --> 00:16:56,620
I need to eat more.

466
00:16:56,740 --> 00:16:57,340
Why so mad?

467
00:16:57,340 --> 00:16:58,580
Who made you angry?

468
00:16:59,370 --> 00:17:00,830
There was a tourist today.

469
00:17:01,360 --> 00:17:03,240
He said I made the schedule too tight,

470
00:17:03,240 --> 00:17:05,270
and it was so tiring that
he couldn't sleep.

471
00:17:05,270 --> 00:17:07,000
He wanted me to cut out some scenic spots.

472
00:17:07,000 --> 00:17:07,640
I said,

473
00:17:08,660 --> 00:17:09,790
this is a group tour;

474
00:17:09,810 --> 00:17:11,609
it's not just for one person.

475
00:17:12,069 --> 00:17:13,400
-Yeah.
-Before I could finish,

476
00:17:13,400 --> 00:17:14,930
he started arguing with me.

477
00:17:16,660 --> 00:17:17,450
I said, fine,

478
00:17:17,960 --> 00:17:19,700
let's have a meeting together.

479
00:17:19,980 --> 00:17:21,280
If everyone agrees,

480
00:17:21,300 --> 00:17:22,810
I will discuss it with the company.

481
00:17:22,810 --> 00:17:24,000
Guess what he said?

482
00:17:24,770 --> 00:17:26,030
"Don't discuss it with me.

483
00:17:26,030 --> 00:17:28,000
I pay, so you just listen to me."

484
00:17:28,160 --> 00:17:28,870
Right?

485
00:17:29,110 --> 00:17:30,350
He was just that bossy.

486
00:17:30,350 --> 00:17:31,720
You acted exactly like him.

487
00:17:31,720 --> 00:17:33,160
I could just guess.

488
00:17:33,220 --> 00:17:35,220
Rich people are all bossy like that.

489
00:17:35,680 --> 00:17:36,980
When I get rich,

490
00:17:38,220 --> 00:17:39,570
I'll let you be that bossy too.

491
00:17:39,570 --> 00:17:40,920
Next time you meet someone like this,

492
00:17:40,920 --> 00:17:41,790
just tell him,

493
00:17:42,270 --> 00:17:43,460
"If you don't have money,

494
00:17:43,460 --> 00:17:44,630
join a group tour

495
00:17:44,960 --> 00:17:45,940
and listen to the guide.

496
00:17:45,940 --> 00:17:48,070
If you have money, get a private tour."

497
00:17:49,310 --> 00:17:50,910
Let him do whatever he wants.

498
00:17:52,050 --> 00:17:53,050
Are you happy now?

499
00:17:55,560 --> 00:17:56,790
Still a little angry.

500
00:17:57,400 --> 00:17:57,830
Well...

501
00:17:57,830 --> 00:17:59,760
How about you cheer me up a bit more?

502
00:17:59,940 --> 00:18:00,180
What?

503
00:18:00,180 --> 00:18:00,680
You want me to

504
00:18:00,680 --> 00:18:01,920
put on a performance?

505
00:18:02,010 --> 00:18:02,890
That'll be nice.

506
00:18:02,890 --> 00:18:04,880
You reacted quite fast.

507
00:18:05,310 --> 00:18:06,330
It's the middle of the night.

508
00:18:06,330 --> 00:18:07,300
I can't play the sax

509
00:18:07,300 --> 00:18:08,540
or the guitar.

510
00:18:09,660 --> 00:18:10,120
How about

511
00:18:10,120 --> 00:18:11,350
I do a kip-up for you?

512
00:18:11,400 --> 00:18:12,160
Sure.

513
00:18:13,180 --> 00:18:14,070
I want to see.

514
00:18:14,420 --> 00:18:15,480
Come on.

515
00:18:15,550 --> 00:18:17,420
Just show me.

516
00:18:19,990 --> 00:18:20,680
Alright.

517
00:18:21,220 --> 00:18:22,480
Sit on the windowsill.

518
00:18:22,640 --> 00:18:23,200
Okay.

519
00:18:23,200 --> 00:18:25,060
Eat while you watch.

520
00:18:29,220 --> 00:18:30,480
Here comes the kip-up.

521
00:18:40,160 --> 00:18:40,740
Hurry up.

522
00:18:49,300 --> 00:18:50,480
I'm gathering my energy.

523
00:18:50,480 --> 00:18:51,430
Wait a moment.

524
00:18:51,550 --> 00:18:52,550
Watch carefully.

525
00:19:01,530 --> 00:19:02,310
How was it?

526
00:19:02,500 --> 00:19:03,140
Awesome.

527
00:19:04,070 --> 00:19:05,830
I swear, a Beijing boy

528
00:19:05,960 --> 00:19:07,110
can't handle compliments.

529
00:19:07,110 --> 00:19:08,140
Once you praise me...

530
00:19:08,140 --> 00:19:09,530
Do another one.

531
00:19:09,700 --> 00:19:10,530
Another one?

532
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:12,170
Okay, another one.

533
00:19:12,940 --> 00:19:14,130
Another one.

534
00:19:14,770 --> 00:19:15,680
Another one.

535
00:19:18,270 --> 00:19:20,090
Kip-up plus a forward roll.

536
00:19:20,160 --> 00:19:20,750
Great!

537
00:19:25,750 --> 00:19:26,680
Are you alright?

538
00:19:27,720 --> 00:19:28,420
I'm fine.

539
00:19:30,700 --> 00:19:31,900
I just got up too fast.

540
00:19:32,430 --> 00:19:33,530
My head is a little dizzy.

541
00:19:33,530 --> 00:19:34,390
Be careful.

542
00:19:34,420 --> 00:19:35,550
I'm fine. It's okay.

543
00:19:36,180 --> 00:19:36,980
Well...

544
00:19:38,740 --> 00:19:41,350
Then you're not going to
cheer me up anymore?

545
00:19:42,290 --> 00:19:43,170
I've done enough cheering.

546
00:19:43,170 --> 00:19:44,230
What if I get angry?

547
00:19:44,230 --> 00:19:45,960
How are you going to cheer me up?

548
00:19:46,970 --> 00:19:48,990
Honey Liangliang,

549
00:19:49,030 --> 00:19:50,710
you are the best.

550
00:19:55,250 --> 00:19:56,550
Isn't this making me going to heaven?

551
00:19:56,550 --> 00:19:58,560
A Beijing boy can't stand this.

552
00:19:58,750 --> 00:20:00,150
Go sit on the windowsill.

553
00:20:00,720 --> 00:20:01,790
I'll do a flip for you.

554
00:20:01,790 --> 00:20:02,610
Yay!

555
00:20:02,640 --> 00:20:04,000
It's not a kip-up anymore,

556
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:04,880
it's a flip.

557
00:20:04,880 --> 00:20:05,550
Watch.

558
00:20:05,750 --> 00:20:07,100
1, 2, 3.

559
00:20:10,510 --> 00:20:11,200
How was it?

560
00:20:11,680 --> 00:20:12,550
Another one.

561
00:20:13,720 --> 00:20:14,710
Backflip.

562
00:20:18,090 --> 00:20:18,610
This...

563
00:20:20,380 --> 00:20:21,420
Your hair is all messy.

564
00:20:21,420 --> 00:20:21,770
Well...

565
00:20:21,770 --> 00:20:22,960
I just got up too fast.

566
00:20:22,960 --> 00:20:24,400
My head is just a little dizzy.

567
00:20:24,400 --> 00:20:26,810
This act is over.

568
00:20:26,810 --> 00:20:27,810
There is one more,

569
00:20:28,380 --> 00:20:29,370
a bonus act.

570
00:20:31,000 --> 00:20:31,850
Do you want to see it?

571
00:20:31,850 --> 00:20:32,580
Or maybe not.

572
00:20:32,720 --> 00:20:34,080
No, I want to see it.

573
00:20:34,110 --> 00:20:34,520
Okay.

574
00:20:34,550 --> 00:20:36,880
The next is a disappearing act.

575
00:20:42,030 --> 00:20:42,610
What are you doing?

576
00:20:42,610 --> 00:20:44,340
Why did you take off your socks?

577
00:20:44,510 --> 00:20:45,700
What are you doing?

578
00:20:46,920 --> 00:20:48,070
It hurts.

579
00:20:48,680 --> 00:20:49,940
Look, it hurts me.

580
00:20:51,900 --> 00:20:53,240
Zhuang Zhuang, hurry up.

581
00:20:53,240 --> 00:20:55,720
This is your favorite flatfish.

582
00:20:55,740 --> 00:20:56,090
Look.

583
