they should report them promptly.

873
00:35:22,710 --> 00:35:23,470
Also,

874
00:35:23,730 --> 00:35:24,330
should we

875
00:35:24,360 --> 00:35:25,360
go to the factory?

876
00:35:25,710 --> 00:35:27,000
I'm worried something went wrong

877
00:35:27,000 --> 00:35:27,820
on their end.

878
00:35:30,320 --> 00:35:30,900
Okay.

879
00:35:31,280 --> 00:35:32,530
With the work stopped suddenly,

880
00:35:32,530 --> 00:35:33,870
many people are worried

881
00:35:33,980 --> 00:35:35,320
that their previous efforts were in vain.

882
00:35:35,320 --> 00:35:36,280
As you know,

883
00:35:36,510 --> 00:35:38,410
the workers' wages are based on

884
00:35:38,460 --> 00:35:40,520
a basic salary plus piece-rate pay.

885
00:35:40,650 --> 00:35:43,590
It was supposed to be a good thing
where more work means more pay.

886
00:35:43,590 --> 00:35:44,850
With this suspension,

887
00:35:45,030 --> 00:35:46,430
many people have asked me

888
00:35:49,650 --> 00:35:51,450
if they'll eventually get paid.

889
00:35:51,980 --> 00:35:52,860
They are worried.

890
00:35:52,860 --> 00:35:53,570
Ren,

891
00:35:53,760 --> 00:35:55,110
don't worry about that.

892
00:35:55,350 --> 00:35:56,530
You know what kind of

893
00:35:56,550 --> 00:35:57,350
people we are.

894
00:35:57,610 --> 00:35:59,610
We won't short anyone a single cent.

895
00:35:59,800 --> 00:36:00,800
That's good then.

896
00:36:01,780 --> 00:36:03,690
I saw the news report from a few days ago.

897
00:36:03,690 --> 00:36:04,690
About Russia boycotting

898
00:36:04,690 --> 00:36:05,950
Chinese down jackets.

899
00:36:06,010 --> 00:36:06,730
I saw our clothes

900
00:36:06,730 --> 00:36:07,940
on the news.

901
00:36:08,210 --> 00:36:09,540
Our brand label

902
00:36:09,560 --> 00:36:10,960
was prominently displayed.

903
00:36:10,960 --> 00:36:13,300
The clothes were piled up and burned.

904
00:36:13,920 --> 00:36:14,360
I mean,

905
00:36:14,380 --> 00:36:15,780
what exactly is going on?

906
00:36:16,420 --> 00:36:18,030
The situation in Russia

907
00:36:18,150 --> 00:36:19,090
didn't just happen

908
00:36:19,090 --> 00:36:20,010
overnight.

909
00:36:20,610 --> 00:36:21,780
It's been building up for a long time

910
00:36:21,780 --> 00:36:23,440
and just exploded all at once.

911
00:36:26,510 --> 00:36:27,760
They don't make things properly,

912
00:36:27,760 --> 00:36:28,720
and in the end,

913
00:36:29,000 --> 00:36:30,730
it hurts all Chinese goods.

914
00:36:30,860 --> 00:36:32,160
It screwed us over too,

915
00:36:32,280 --> 00:36:32,980
right?

916
00:36:33,190 --> 00:36:35,190
Let's just have a good New Year first

917
00:36:35,230 --> 00:36:36,920
and try to start work again
after the New Year.

918
00:36:36,920 --> 00:36:38,560
Just set your mind at ease,

919
00:36:38,620 --> 00:36:39,690
and help us control the quality.

920
00:36:39,690 --> 00:36:40,350
That'll do.

921
00:36:41,900 --> 00:36:43,160
Okay, don't worry.

922
00:37:22,460 --> 00:37:23,450
You're back.

923
00:37:23,760 --> 00:37:25,220
Hurry up. Wash up and rest.

924
00:37:25,320 --> 00:37:26,540
Okay, honey.

925
00:37:27,010 --> 00:37:28,210
You go ahead and rest.

926
00:37:29,310 --> 00:37:30,300
Honey.

927
00:37:31,400 --> 00:37:32,710
I sold

928
00:37:32,740 --> 00:37:34,080
60 down jackets today.

929
00:37:36,090 --> 00:37:37,250
You are amazing.

930
00:37:39,050 --> 00:37:40,060
Nothing amazing.

931
00:37:51,980 --> 00:37:53,310
Every little bit helps.

932
00:38:00,000 --> 00:38:01,260
How much did you drink?

933
00:38:01,960 --> 00:38:02,880
Not much.

934
00:38:04,200 --> 00:38:04,690
Director Yang

935
00:38:04,690 --> 00:38:05,830
called me today.

936
00:38:06,860 --> 00:38:09,000
He said you withdrew money
from the shoe factory again.

937
00:38:09,000 --> 00:38:10,440
He also said you've been
socializing a lot lately

938
00:38:10,440 --> 00:38:11,310
and asked me to take care of you.

939
00:38:11,310 --> 00:38:12,900
Well, since we are doing business,

940
00:38:12,900 --> 00:38:14,700
socializing is totally normal.

941
00:38:14,710 --> 00:38:15,640
But this Yang,

942
00:38:15,670 --> 00:38:16,390
I told him

943
00:38:16,420 --> 00:38:17,670
not to tell you,

944
00:38:18,190 --> 00:38:19,520
but he still did anyway.

945
00:38:20,050 --> 00:38:22,650
How long were you planning
to keep this from me?

946
00:38:35,030 --> 00:38:35,750
Here.

947
00:38:38,460 --> 00:38:39,520
Careful, it's hot.

948
00:38:41,340 --> 00:38:41,900
Is it hot?

949
00:38:45,960 --> 00:38:47,160
Let me take it myself.

950
00:38:56,570 --> 00:38:58,940
When you said the factory would
resume work,

951
00:38:58,940 --> 00:39:01,400
you were planning
to borrow money yourself?

952
00:39:03,320 --> 00:39:04,580
Why didn't you tell me?

953
00:39:07,910 --> 00:39:08,730
Since now

954
00:39:09,780 --> 00:39:11,090
we haven't found any sales channels yet,

955
00:39:11,090 --> 00:39:12,620
telling you would only

956
00:39:13,260 --> 00:39:14,900
make you worry with me.

957
00:39:15,440 --> 00:39:16,320
So you were going to

958
00:39:16,320 --> 00:39:17,360
bear it all alone?

959
00:39:19,510 --> 00:39:21,170
I can handle it. It's nothing.

960
00:39:30,690 --> 00:39:31,170
Do you remember

961
00:39:31,170 --> 00:39:32,300
when my mom was sick?

962
00:39:34,360 --> 00:39:35,880
I only found out

963
00:39:37,150 --> 00:39:37,780
after Jun told me

964
00:39:37,780 --> 00:39:39,580
that your movie didn't get made.

965
00:39:39,670 --> 00:39:41,470
I was so scared after I found out.

966
00:39:41,920 --> 00:39:42,460
I was scared that

967
00:39:42,460 --> 00:39:43,870
if Jun hadn't told me,

968
00:39:44,230 --> 00:39:46,430
if you hadn't come to Wenzhou to find me,

969
00:39:47,830 --> 00:39:49,110
I might never have known

970
00:39:49,110 --> 00:39:50,530
you had such a hard time.

971
00:40:01,840 --> 00:40:02,970
I also blamed myself

972
00:40:05,430 --> 00:40:07,030
that when you needed me most,

973
00:40:08,610 --> 00:40:09,810
I wasn't by your side.

974
00:40:11,530 --> 00:40:13,480
It's fine. It's fine.

975
00:40:17,110 --> 00:40:18,850
So I decided then

976
00:40:20,960 --> 00:40:23,290
that no matter what happens in the future,

977
00:40:24,920 --> 00:40:26,320
we will face it together.

978
00:40:28,130 --> 00:40:28,970
With you here,

979
00:40:30,320 --> 00:40:31,530
even if we have nothing,

980
00:40:31,530 --> 00:40:32,590
the sky won't fall.

981
00:40:41,230 --> 00:40:42,290
Why are you crying?

982
00:40:43,320 --> 00:40:44,060
I'm happy.

983
00:40:46,300 --> 00:40:46,760
Today, I

984
00:40:46,780 --> 00:40:48,680
looked into the details

985
00:40:48,820 --> 00:40:50,220
of mortgaging the house.

986
00:40:50,420 --> 00:40:51,140
The house

987
00:40:51,160 --> 00:40:52,820
can be mortgaged for 250,000.

988
00:40:52,920 --> 00:40:54,780
I also discussed with the factory

989
00:40:55,030 --> 00:40:57,030
the possibility of reducing costs.

990
00:40:57,100 --> 00:40:58,700
I think from now on, we should

991
00:40:59,350 --> 00:41:01,210
sell retail at wholesale prices.

992
00:41:02,150 --> 00:41:04,150
As long as our price is competitive,

993
00:41:04,310 --> 00:41:06,570
our customers will have better margins.

994
00:41:06,900 --> 00:41:08,430
As long as we keep shipping,

995
00:41:08,630 --> 00:41:09,300
the market will definitely

996
00:41:09,300 --> 00:41:10,560
get better gradually.

997
00:41:15,690 --> 00:41:17,420
But you love this house so much.

998
00:41:20,030 --> 00:41:20,710
All right.

999
00:41:22,340 --> 00:41:23,140
I support you.

1000
00:41:24,010 --> 00:41:25,610
It doesn't matter if we make money or not.

1001
00:41:25,610 --> 00:41:27,350
We have to win the market back.

1002
00:41:30,000 --> 00:41:32,200
We'll fight this long battle together.

1003
00:41:32,960 --> 00:41:33,690
Let's fight.

1004
00:41:35,500 --> 00:41:37,000
If we win this time...

1005
00:41:37,030 --> 00:41:38,090
We'll get married.

1006
00:41:45,880 --> 00:41:47,490
What if we lose?

1007
00:41:47,900 --> 00:41:49,300
We'll still get married.

1008
00:42:02,010 --> 00:42:03,730
There's this popular term these days.

1009
00:42:03,730 --> 00:42:04,790
What was it called?

1010
00:42:05,570 --> 00:42:06,770
"Beijing drifters."

1011
00:42:09,530 --> 00:42:10,730
We are so young.

1012
00:42:13,230 --> 00:42:16,160
Worst case, we start over
as Beijing drifters again.

1013
00:42:17,150 --> 00:42:17,730
Drift.

1014
00:42:18,980 --> 00:42:20,150
We can drift anywhere,

1015
00:42:20,150 --> 00:42:21,550
as long as you are with me.

1016
00:42:27,000 --> 00:42:28,430
I've also figured it out.

1017
00:42:30,140 --> 00:42:32,640
Whether the house is rented

1018
00:42:32,670 --> 00:42:33,640
or bought.

1019
00:42:35,010 --> 00:42:38,000
whether we're poor or rich,

1020
00:42:39,070 --> 00:42:41,210
our life together is our own.

1021
00:42:42,570 --> 00:42:44,970
I have the determination
to make you happy.

1022
00:42:49,690 --> 00:42:50,320
Why are you suddenly

1023
00:42:50,320 --> 00:42:51,710
saying wedding vows?

1024
00:42:52,730 --> 00:42:54,710
I've always wanted to marry you.
